VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)\b(apikey|api(?:-|_)?key|secret|token|access_token|auth_token|client_secret|private_key|encryption_key|db_password|security_key|session_key|service_account_key|passphrase|cert_key|app_secret|api_secret|jwt_secret)\b\s*[:=]\s*["'][^"']{8,}["']
WHEN EXPR MISSING:(?i)\b(example|sample|dummy|test|placeholder|mock|getenv|env\(|secretsmanager|vault|kms|buildconfig|gradle\.properties)\b
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects potential server-side secrets handling vulnerabilities in the code.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Server-side Secrets Handling.
